    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! \ud83d\ude97 This ride has been absolutely wonderful to me\u2014it's super reliable, runs smoothly, and has been really well-loved. It's in great shape and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some fun adventures. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! I'm happy to answer any questions you have or set up a time for you to see it in person. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers a linear torque curve and an 8,400 RPM redline, mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement with VAC-treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, and the M-variable limited-slip differential provides optimal lock-up. While the aesthetic condition shows minor patina consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain dialed for peak lateral acceleration. A turn-key example for the driver prioritizing mechanical performance over showroom perfection.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs smoothly. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that serves as a perfect example of a reliable, high-quality daily driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, though close inspection reveals minor, typical road wear such as small stone chips on the lower front valance. The body panels are straight with consistent gaps throughout. Inside, the cabin remains a highlight; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, the dashboard is crack-free, and all electronic features\u2014including the premium audio system and dual-zone climate control\u2014work perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet. It has benefited from a strict maintenance schedule, including a recent cooling system flush and a fresh set of tires with excellent tread remaining. The transmission shifts crisply, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride without any unusual noises. This is a non-smoker, pet-free vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. It comes with a complete set of service records and two sets of keys, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who prioritizes both performance and sustained value. It exhibits a commendable standard of maintenance, featuring a robust powertrain and an interior cabin that remains in superior order. Rigorously inspected to ensure operational excellence, this offering provides a sophisticated driving experience and represents a prudent investment for those seeking a reliable, high-caliber motorcar.",
      "price": 31900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid, dependable shape and has been well-cared for, so it's totally ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend trips! I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale, so feel free to reach out with any questions. I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
