      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear, aggressive power band. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates and upgraded polyurethane bushings to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its original geometry but benefits from refreshed dampers and control arms, maintaining the communicative feedback these cars are known for. While the exterior displays minor stone chips and age-appropriate patina, the mechanical synchronization is excellent, with a recent valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. This is a driver-focused example where performance and drivetrain integrity take center stage.",
      "price": 34500.0,
